00:13:34,599 --> 00:13:38,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么？我怎么说谎了？</font>

167
00:13:38,829 --> 00:13:43,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你是艾丽西亚的防卫本能所产生出的全新生命</font>

168
00:13:45,049 --> 00:13:49,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">最开始继承SPES能力和意志的人是艾丽西亚</font>

169
00:13:49,709 --> 00:13:53,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以你拼命地想要接近SPES</font>

170
00:13:53,969 --> 00:13:54,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过是个…</font>

171
00:13:55,229 --> 00:13:56,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">冒牌货罢了</font>

172
00:14:03,829 --> 00:14:06,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那你说我为何要这么做？</font>

173
00:14:07,929 --> 00:14:10,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我又为何要如此忠诚于SPES？</font>

174
00:14:11,239 --> 00:14:12,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你只是在渴求着爱吧</font>

175
00:14:14,569 --> 00:14:15,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">来自父亲的爱</font>

176
00:14:16,689 --> 00:14:19,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你只是想被父亲所爱</font>

177
00:14:19,999 --> 00:14:21,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">想被别人认可</font>

178
00:14:22,459 --> 00:14:23,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">仅此而已</font>

179
00:14:23,529 --> 00:14:24,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不对！</font>

180
00:14:31,369 --> 00:14:37,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刚才 你和艾丽西亚交换人格 是为了让她承受痛苦</font>

181
00:14:37,799 --> 00:14:40,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为你嫉妒艾丽西亚</font>

182
00:14:41,889 --> 00:14:42,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说什么…</font>

183
00:14:43,049 --> 00:14:45,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">明明你一直在承受痛苦</font>

184
00:14:45,529 --> 00:14:48,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但艾丽西亚却找到了我和助手这样的同伴</font>

185
00:14:48,509 --> 00:14:50,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这让你非常憎恨 非常憎恨…</font>

186
00:14:50,919 --> 00:14:52,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又非常羡慕</font>

187
00:14:53,549 --> 00:14:54,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不对！</font>

188
00:14:54,939 --> 00:14:58,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不对…不对…不对！</font>

189
00:14:58,169 --> 00:15:03,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没什么不对 你只是想被人所爱 想要找到同伴</font>

190
00:15:03,119 --> 00:15:04,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">闭嘴！</font>

191
00:15:05,529 --> 00:15:06,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">自相残杀吧</font>

192
00:15:12,069 --> 00:15:14,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔 你是不会死的</font>

193
00:15:16,179 --> 00:15:18,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手 你也不会死</font>

194
00:15:30,279 --> 00:15:31,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么…</font>

195
00:15:32,429 --> 00:15:39,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">很简单 助手比起任何人 甚至比我自己都更值得信任</font>

196
00:15:39,879 --> 00:15:45,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们都信任对方胜过信任自己 就这么简单</font>

197
00:15:46,109 --> 00:15:51,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">搞什么…这样就能让我的力量失效？</font>

198
00:15:51,869 --> 00:15:53,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这什么烂剧本…</font>

199
00:15:54,239 --> 00:15:56,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">至少称之为「牵绊」嘛</font>

200
00:15:56,729 --> 00:15:59,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">牵绊？那种东西…</font>

201
00:15:59,859 --> 00:16:01,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那种东西…</font>

202
00:16:01,419 --> 00:16:04,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">赫尔 你没必要再遵从什么圣典了</font>

203
00:16:05,429 --> 00:16:07,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没必要再杀更多人</font>

204
00:16:08,389 --> 00:16:12,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算不那样做 你也能找到同伴 产生牵绊</font>

205
00:16:13,139 --> 00:16:17,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以没必要勉强自己去听原初之种的…</font>

206
00:16:17,449 --> 00:16:18,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然如此！</font>

207
00:16:19,649 --> 00:16:20,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我就更不能输给你！</font>

208
00:16:22,239 --> 00:16:27,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我承认 我想被人爱 被人需要</font>

209
00:16:28,059 --> 00:16:30,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">想被人认可我出生的意义</font>

210
00:16:31,229 --> 00:16:34,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是 这并不是随便找个人就行了的</font>

211
00:16:35,469 --> 00:16:40,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只为了父亲而活 而战 去毁灭世界</font>

212
00:16:41,319 --> 00:16:44,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这就是我的生存本能</font>

213
00:16:44,999 --> 00:16:48,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好吧 也该分出胜负了</font>

214
00:16:49,629 --> 00:16:51,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就来做个了结吧</font>

215
00:16:59,389 --> 00:17:00,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这次又怎么了？</font>

216
00:17:12,809 --> 00:17:13,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手！</font>

217
00:17:32,399 --> 00:17:33,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">女士！</font>

218
00:17:48,359 --> 00:17:53,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">它原本应该被关在研究所里 是被食物的味道吸引来的吧</font>

219
00:18:00,249 --> 00:18:00,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔！</font>

220
00:18:05,109 --> 00:18:08,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你就暂时别动吧</font>

221
00:18:13,399 --> 00:18:15,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">血有点流得太多了</font>

222
00:18:21,499 --> 00:18:24,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">必须换新的才行</font>

223
00:18:29,419 --> 00:18:30,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">住手！</font>

224
00:18:30,729 --> 00:18:35,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">想要心脏的话 我可以给你！所以放过她…</font>

225
00:18:35,959 --> 00:18:37,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">放过谢丝塔吧！</font>

226
00:18:38,809 --> 00:18:40,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我之前说过</font>

227
00:18:40,759 --> 00:18:48,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你将来会成为我的搭档 所以要珍惜性命哦</font>

228
00:18:54,329 --> 00:18:58,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大侦探的心脏归我了</font>

229
00:19:01,349 --> 00:19:06,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">终于得到配得上这个身体的心脏了</font>

230
00:19:06,619 --> 00:19:08,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这样父亲肯定也会…</font>

231
00:19:11,639 --> 00:19:12,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还给我…</font>

232
00:19:16,469 --> 00:19:20,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那心脏是谢丝塔的 还给我！</font>

233
00:19:22,039 --> 00:19:26,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那可做不到 已经是我的东西了</font>

234
00:19:26,759 --> 00:19:29,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不许用你的脏手碰谢丝塔！</font>

235
00:19:32,569 --> 00:19:34,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你的拳头碰不到我</font>

236
00:19:40,869 --> 00:19:47,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你的愤怒从何而来？是你刚才说的 你们的「牵绊」？</font>

237
00:19:47,979 --> 00:19:50,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你又是她的什么人呢？</font>

238
00:19:54,139 --> 00:19:58,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不用赫尔问 我也一直在思考这件事</font>

239
00:19:59,149 --> 00:20:01,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我到底是谢丝塔的什么人</font>

240
00:20:02,169 --> 00:20:05,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对谢丝塔来说 我到底算什么</font>

241
00:20:06,199 --> 00:20:06,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是</font>

242
00:20:09,479 --> 00:20:11,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在已经无从知晓了</font>

243
00:20:16,999 --> 00:20:17,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即使如此…</font>

244
00:20:19,719 --> 00:20:26,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">自从在1万米的高空相识 我们已经一起旅行了3年</font>

245
00:20:27,279 --> 00:20:29,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那段日子绝对算不上安稳</font>

246
00:20:30,229 --> 00:20:35,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">无数次濒临死亡 被她骂愚蠢 面临不讲道理的对待…</font>

247
00:20:36,719 --> 00:20:42,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是 1千次不讲道理的遭遇 却能让我笑出来1万次</font>

248
00:20:43,569 --> 00:20:45,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">都是和谢丝塔一起欢笑</font>

249
00:20:49,789 --> 00:20:53,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">问我和谢丝塔是什么关系？</font>

250
00:20:54,939 --> 00:20:58,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">问我对谢丝塔有什么想法？</font>

251
00:21:00,139 --> 00:21:02,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这些事情 我一开始就知道得很清楚！</font>

252
00:21:03,479 --> 00:21:07,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">当然是世界上最重要的人啊！</font>

253
00:21:18,189 --> 00:21:20,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么…回事…</font>

254
00:21:38,099 --> 00:21:41,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢…丝…塔…</font>

255
00:22:03,249 --> 00:22:04,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">之前那是…</font>

256
00:22:06,489 --> 00:22:11,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">每次醒来 你都在我身边</font>

257
00:22:11,859 --> 00:22:17,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我一个全新的早晨</font>

258
00:22:17,009 --> 00:22:22,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那心跳是如此温柔</font>

259
00:22:22,389 --> 00:22:27,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又悲伤得催人泪下</font>

260
00:22:27,709 --> 00:22:32,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在大声叫喊著 想要见到某人</font>

261
00:22:33,059 --> 00:22:38,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又不知道名字和长相</font>

262
00:22:38,389 --> 00:22:43,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我真的听到了那声音</font>

263
00:22:43,709 --> 00:22:48,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只能漫无目的地去探寻</font>

264
00:22:48,669 --> 00:22:53,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然可能只会徒增烦恼</font>

265
00:22:54,009 --> 00:23:02,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这不是为了别人而是为了自己</font>

266
00:23:03,849 --> 00:23:09,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">胸膛中的声音 那声呐喊 指引着我前进</font>

267
00:23:09,149 --> 00:23:14,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将零落的心意捡起 送到它想去的地方吧</font>

268
00:23:14,469 --> 00:23:19,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为是你告诉我生命的意义</font>

269
00:23:19,719 --> 00:23:27,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我觉得 这个世界也许还没那么坏</font>

270
00:23:35,969 --> 00:23:40,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第10集 所以我当不了侦探)</font>

